ComicInfo.Title: To Become An Immortal!; There Shall Come a Miracle!
ComicInfo.Summary:
To Become An Immortal!: Jane fails Odin's test for immortality and is sent back to Earth with no memory of Thor or Asgard. Thor encounters the goddess Sif, Heimdall's sister, after many years.
There Shall Come a Miracle!: Thor and companions defeat Fafnir and return life to the land of Nastrond.
